{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idaa1d3e3e-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3305"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3305"},"text":"§ 3305.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Pre-award debriefings","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaa1d3e3f-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3305/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Request for Debriefing","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"When the contracting officer excludes an offeror submitting a competitive proposal from the competitive range (or otherwise excludes such an offeror from further consideration prior to the final source selection decision), the excluded offeror may request in writing, within three days after the date on which the excluded offeror receives notice of its exclusion, a debriefing prior to award.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaa1d3e40-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3305/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"When Debriefing to Be Conducted","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The contracting officer shall make every effort to debrief the unsuccessful offeror as soon as practicable but may refuse the request for a debriefing if it is not in the best interests of the Government to conduct a debriefing at that time.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaa1d3e41-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3305/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Precondition for Post-award Debriefing","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The contracting officer is required to debrief an excluded offeror in accordance with ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s3304"},"text":"section 3304 of this title","children":[],"tail":" only if that offeror requested and was refused a preaward debriefing under subsections (a) and (b)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaa1d3e42-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3305/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Information to Be Provided","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The debriefing conducted under subsections (a) and (b) shall include—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa1d3e43-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3305/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the executive agency’s evaluation of the significant elements in the offeror’s offer;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa1d3e44-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3305/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a summary of the rationale for the offeror’s exclusion; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa1d3e45-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3305/d/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" reasonable responses to relevant questions posed by the debriefed offeror as to whether source selection procedures set forth in the solicitation, applicable regulations, and other applicable authorities were followed by the executive agency.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaa1d3e46-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3305/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Information Not to Be Disclosed","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The debriefing conducted under subsections (a) and (b) may not disclose the number or identity of other offerors and shall not disclose information about the content, ranking, or evaluation of other offerors’ proposals.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaa1d3e47-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3305/f"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"f"},"text":"(f)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Summary to Be Included in File","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The contracting officer shall include a summary of any debriefing conducted under this section in the contract file.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idaa1d3e48-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added and amended ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/283/dA/tXVIII/s1816/c/2/E"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–283, div. A, title XVIII, § 1816(c)(2)(E)","children":[],"tail":", (7), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 2021","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/134/4182"},"text":"134 Stat. 4182","children":[],"tail":", 4183; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/81/dA/tXVII/s1701/b/6/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–81, div. A, title XVII, § 1701(b)(6)(B)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-12-27"},"text":"Dec. 27, 2021","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/135/2133"},"text":"135 Stat. 2133","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idaa1d3e49-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idaa1d3e4a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idaa1d3e4b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The text of subsec. (b)(6) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2305"},"text":"section 2305 of this title","children":[],"tail":", which was transferred to this section, redesignated as subsecs. (a) to (e), and amended by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/283/s1816/c/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–283, § 1816(c)(1)","children":[],"tail":", (2)(E), (7)(A), (C)–(I), was based on "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/106/dD/tXLI/s4104/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–106, div. D, title XLI, § 4104(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-02-10"},"text":"Feb. 10, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/644"},"text":"110 Stat. 644","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/201/dA/tX/s1074/a/11"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–201, div. A, title X, § 1074(a)(11)","childre